" +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\"(+) = ? " +" and T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\"(+) = ? " +" and M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" = 1"

"select " +" M_PLANT.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", 0), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"from " +" M_PLANT, " +" M_WH, " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK " +"where " +" M_PLANT.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD " +" and M_PLANT.WH_CD = T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.WH_CD(+) " +" and M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\"(+) = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\"(+) = ? " +" and T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\"(+) = ? " +" and M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" = 1"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(THIS_MONTH, 'YYYY/MM'), 'YYYY/MM') AS THIS_MONTH " +"FROM " +" SYS_DEBT_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ( " +" SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD " +" FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" WHERE " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" )"
"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(INSTALL_FLG) AS INSTALL_FLG " +"FROM " +" SYS_INSTALL_OPTIONS " +"WHERE " +" OPTION_ID = 'C*'"
"SELECT " +" VALUE " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"WHERE " +" NAME = ?"
"SELECT " +" PROC_EXEC_DATE " +"FROM " +" SYS_ACTUAL_COST_CTRL_AC " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ?"

"select " +" T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO " +"from " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"where " +" T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD"

"select " +" T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD, " +" T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO, " +" to_char(T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, " +" to_char(T_LOT_STOCK.DEFECT_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as DEFECT_QTY, " +" to_char((T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY - T_LOT_STOCK.ALCD_QTY), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as ALLOCABLE_QTY, " +" T_LOT_CTRL.EXTERNAL_LOT_NO, " +" to_char(T_LOT_CTRL.BEST_BEFORE_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') as BEST_BEFORE_DATE, " +" to_char(T_LOT_CTRL.PRD_CMPLT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') as PRD_CMPLT_DATE, " +" M_ITEM.STOCK_UNIT, " +" M_WH.WH_NAME, " +" M_WH.WH_TYP " +"from " +" T_LOT_STOCK, " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD " +" and M_WH.MRP_FLG = 1 " +" and(T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY - T_LOT_STOCK.ALCD_QTY) <> 0 " +"order by " +" T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD, " +" T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO"

"select " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO as LOT_NO, " +" to_char(T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as ISSUE_QTY, " +" to_char((T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_QTY - T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.SPENT_QTY), 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as SPENT_QTY, " +" M_ITEM.STOCK_UNIT as STOCK_UNIT " +"from " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +"order by " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO"

"SELECT " +" NVL(CASE WHEN TO_DATE(?,'YYYY/MM/DD') > T_LOT_CTRL.BEST_BEFORE_DATE " +" THEN '1' ELSE '0' END, 0) BBD_c_FLG " +"FROM " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD " +" AND T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO = ? " +" AND T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_QTY) AS ISSUE_QTY " +"FROM " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO = ? " +"FOR UPDATE NOWAIT"

"insert into " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST(\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", \\"LOT_NO\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", \\"ISSUE_QTY\\", \\"ISSUE_DATE\\", \\"SPENT_QTY\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_DATE(?), 0)"

"update " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST " +"set " +" \\"ISSUE_QTY\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"ISSUE_DATE\\" = to_date(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD') " +"where " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.LOT_NO = ?"

"select " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(SUM(T_LOT_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\"), 0), 'TM9') as \\"TOTAL_STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"from " +" T_LOT_STOCK, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_LOT_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" " +" and M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" = 1"

"SELECT " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" AS \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" AS \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" AS \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" AS \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" AS \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" DECODE(T3.LOT_CTRL_FLG, 1, NVL(T1.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, 0) - NVL(T2.ALCD_QTY, 0), NVL(T1.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, 0)) AS UN_ALC_STOCK " +"FROM " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" SUM(NVL(A.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY, 0)) AS STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY " +" FROM " +" T_ITEM_STOCK A " +" WHERE " +" A.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND A.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND A.WH_CD in ( " +" select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" " +" from " +" M_WH " +" where " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" = 1 " +" ) " +" ) T1, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" SUM(NVL(B.ALCD_QTY, 0)) AS ALCD_QTY " +" FROM " +" T_LOT_CTRL A, " +" T_LOT_STOCK B " +" WHERE " +" A.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND B.ITEM_CD = A.ITEM_CD " +" AND B.LOT_NO = A.LOT_NO " +" AND B.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND B.\\"WH_CD\\" in ( " +" select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" " +" from " +" M_WH " +" where " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" = 1 " +" ) " +" ) T2, " +" M_ITEM T3 " +"WHERE " +" T3.ITEM_CD = ?"

"select " +" nvl(SUM(A.ALCD_QTY), 0) AS ALCD_QTY " +"from " +" T_LOT_STOCK A, " +" M_ITEM B, " +" M_WH C " +"where " +" C.MRP_FLG = 1 " +" AND A.WH_CD = C.WH_CD " +" AND B.LOT_CTRL_FLG = 1 " +" AND A.ITEM_CD = B.ITEM_CD " +" AND A.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND A.ITEM_CD = ?"

"select " +" count(1) " +"from " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_OD, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC, " +" T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_PROC.WORK_IN_PROC_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = T_WORK_IN_PROC_BY_ITEM.WORK_ODR_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WORK_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\" = 2 " +" and M_ITEM.\\"LOT_CTRL_FLG\\" = ? " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"select " +" count(1) " +"from " +" T_LOT_STOCK, " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_LOT_CTRL, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = T_LOT_CTRL.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = T_LOT_CTRL.LOT_NO(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.LOT_NO = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_STOCK.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD " +" and M_WH.MRP_FLG = 1 " +" and(T_LOT_STOCK.STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY - T_LOT_STOCK.ALCD_QTY) <> 0 " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"select " +" count(1) " +"from " +" T_LOT_ISSUE_INST, " +" T_ISSUE_INST, " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +" and T_LOT_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD = T_ISSUE_INST.ISSUE_INST_CD " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.ITEM_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.WORK_ODR_CD = ? " +" and T_ISSUE_INST.PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"select " +" proc.work_in_proc_cd " +"from " +" t_work_in_proc_by_proc proc, " +" ( " +" select " +" min(t.proc_no) as proc_no_a " +" from " +" t_work_in_proc_by_proc t " +" where " +" t.work_odr_cd = ? " +" and t.outside_typ = 1 " +" ) A " +"where " +" proc.work_odr_cd = ? " +" and proc.proc_no = A.proc_no_a " +" and proc.outside_typ = 1"
